column5: We got the boat in the water today... all went well with a great night of fishing.  We went 9 for 12        We fished from about 6pm till 11pm and caught all of our fish on cut bait and large emeral shinners.  On the way back in we were marking fish all over the place...
Good to see what we have instore for us tomorrow and on the 18th. Will see you tomorrow at 9am
some bruiser felines !!  even the smaller cats that i've tangled with were incredible on the fight -meter.  those bad boyz must have left a mark!  very impressive!
Oh man I ame really getting wound up for the 19th!  AILE GOBY;  unless I'm confused, our group trip is the 19th, not the 18th (or are you going both days).
Great report and pics Fishmaster  Looks like you guys had fun.... Good looking cats Thanks for sharing Leechman
thanks for the invite    lol. i like catching fish too ya know! good job on the kittys, see ya tomorrow bud!

I got there as fishmaster was pulling a bucket full of huge cats from the boat..I guess your not fishmaster for no reason ...ooh yea did I mention your a fishmaster LOL  ....seriously want to thank your wife for the great service in the bait~shop Very knowledgeable and courteous and I called about my net but a member on this site grabbed it for me.....thanks again  I will be back ! ( thought I'd give you fair warning )
Yes my bad the 19th i always forget
